Source of truth (read from `.ai-rules/`):

- `architecture.md`
- `api.md`
- `database.md`
- `security.md`
- `testing.md`
- `workers.md` (when the target repo uses background jobs)

Replace glob paths in this file when adopting into a repository with a different layout.
